## Academic Use Notice

This project was developed as part of a Final Year University Project for 
academic and educational purposes. 

### For Academic Citation:
If you use this work in your research or academic work, please provide 
appropriate attribution:

```
Asfund Yar Khan. (2026). UK Financial Early Warning System: A Machine Learning 
Approach to Predicting Market Stress. Final Year Project, University of Hertfordshire.
Available at: https://github.com/asfundyarkhan/uk-financial-ews
```

### Data Attribution:
- Financial data sourced from Yahoo Finance
- News data sourced from CNBC Financial News
